<body>

    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>AI传术师俱乐部 | 生财有术</h1>
            <p>2025年06月23日 聊天精华报告</p>
        </header>

        <main>
            <div class="bento-grid">
                <div class="card grid-col-span-4">
                    <h2 class="card-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-pie"></i>本日概览</h2>
                    <ul class="stats-list">
                        <li><span><i class="fa-solid fa-comments"></i> 有效消息总数</span> <strong>76 条</strong></li>
                        <li><span><i class="fa-solid fa-users"></i> 活跃用户数</span> <strong>25 人</strong></li>
                        <li><span><i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i> 时间范围</span> <strong>09:28 - 23:55</strong></li>
                        <li><span><i class="fa-solid fa-fire"></i> 讨论焦点</span> <strong>Prompt工程哲学</strong></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="card grid-col-span-8">
                    <h2 class="card-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-simple"></i>发言时段分布</h2>
                    <canvas id="hourlyActivityChart"></canvas>
                </div>

                <div class="card grid-col-span-5">
                    <h2 class="card-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-bullhorn"></i>活跃发言人</h2>
                    <canvas id="topSpeakersChart"></canvas>
                </div>

                <div class="card grid-col-span-7">
                    <h2 class="card-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-tags"></i>核心关键词</h2>
                    <div class="keyword-tags">
                        <span class="keyword-tag">Prompt工程</span>
                        <span class="keyword-tag">结构化提示词</span>
                        <span class="keyword-tag">AI能力边界</span>
